  "one_line_review": "\"A great review gathering tool.\"",
  "detailed_review": "<p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you like best about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">Text message review prompts are very helpful. I also like the review links to google and facebook.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What do you dislike about Synup?</strong></p><p id=\"\">The email review gathering doesn't seem to work very well. I'm not sure if emails are sent to spam, but nobody seems to open them.</p><p id=\"\">‍</p><p id=\"\"><strong id=\"\">What problems is Synup solving and how is that benefiting you?</strong></p><p id=\"\">Review gathering.</p>",
